{"schemaVersion":1,"source":"docfx-mref-page","file":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer.yml","symbols":[{"uid":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer","name":"OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer","fullName":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer","kind":"Class","namespace":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web","assembly":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web","summary":"Enhances operation documentation with automatically generated summaries and descriptions.","remarks":"This transformer automatically generates clear, user-friendly summaries for API operations based on their operation IDs and path information. It respects existing summaries set via XML documentation but fills in gaps for endpoints that lack documentation. Key responsibilities: Generates summaries from operation IDs if not already documentedConverts HTTP method names (Get, Post, Put, Delete, Patch) to readable descriptionsPreserves existing XML documentation summariesImproves API usability and self-discovery in documentation tools Example transformations: GetById \u2192 \u0022Get a single item by its identifier\u0022CreateUser \u2192 \u0022Create a new user\u0022UpdateProfile \u2192 \u0022Update an existing profile\u0022DeleteItem \u2192 \u0022Delete the specified item\u0022PatchSettings \u2192 \u0022Partially update settings\u0022","syntax":{"content":"public class OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer : IOpenApiOperationTransformer","parameters":[],"returns":null},"parameters":[],"returns":null,"parent":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web","children":["BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer.#ctor","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.OperationSummaryDocumentTransformer.TransformAsync(Microsoft.OpenApi.OpenApiOperation,Microsoft.AspNetCore.OpenApi.OpenApiOperationTransformerContext,System.Threading.CancellationToken)"],"extensionMethods":["BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web